---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Chain Brief"
  description="Chain Brief is an independent crypto publication covering what's happening in crypto and how it works — clearly, from first principles. Not financial advice."
>
  <article style="max-width:640px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">About Chain Brief</h1>

    <p style="color:var(--brand-muted); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
      <em>Crypto made clear — from first principles to the latest signals.</em>
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What we are</h2>
    <p>Chain Brief is an independent editorial publication covering the crypto ecosystem. We write for two audiences simultaneously:
    readers who are new to crypto and want to understand how it actually works, and readers already in the ecosystem who want a reliable,
    jargon-free read on what's happening week to week.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What we are not</h2>
    <p>We are <strong>not a financial advisory</strong>. Chain Brief never says "buy X" or "sell Y". We do not publish trading signals,
    price predictions, or investment recommendations. Every piece of content carries a clear disclaimer:
    <em>this is not financial advice</em>. We take this seriously.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What you get</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.25rem; color:var(--brand-muted);">
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Daily Market Brief (Mon–Fri)</strong> — news summaries and on-chain context in plain English</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Weekly Deep-Dive</strong> — protocol analysis, ecosystem developments, what moved markets</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Chain 101 (bi-weekly)</strong> — beginner explainers: blockchains, wallets, DeFi, Layer 2s and beyond</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">Editorial principles</h2>
    <p>Independence above all. We don't accept payment for editorial coverage. Sponsors are clearly disclosed
    and kept separate from editorial content. Our job is to be the most reliable independent voice in a space
    full of conflicts of interest — we protect that fiercely.</p>

    <div class="subscribe-bar" style="margin-top:3rem;">
      <h2>Get crypto made clear.</h2>
      <p>Free. Independent. Not financial advice.</p>
      <div class="subscribe-form">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" aria-label="Email address" />
        <button class="btn">Subscribe</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
